The small winged ship deployed its landing legs and crushed some low 
trees while landing. As soon as the engines died away, a rather large 
hatch opened.

Ramiel: So this is what Earth used to be...

Gogolan: It is beautiful... I just can't find out why things turned 
out so badly for this world...

Ramiel: We shall know soon enough. We need to make a conference table.

He turned and saw a huge tree, maybe as big as the ship. He smiled and 
straightened his wings.

Ramiel: Power and Transform!

He transformed to a strange hybrid between an angel and a coyote. As 
soon as he had done that, he rammed the tree. It fell to the ground.

Gogolan: I guess I'm supposed to make the table, right? Aaah... that's 
not fair... I always get the dirty work...

And transformed too, into some sort of bulky metallic angel. The 
pincer on his right arm became a huge claw with which he slashed 
the tree. They now had a perfect table top.

Ramiel: Okay... To forgive myself, I'll get the anti-g motor...
